{"tid":296841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"盧偉聰：香港目前反恐工作形勢「非常嚴峻」   勿過激示威令警力耗散","createTime":"2017-06-25T03:20:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-25T04:36:30.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"71092db8b840a245aecc2bea3fbf817d49c4e3d7","tid":296841,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T03:20:32.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】傳媒廣泛報道支那國家主席習近平將於下周訪港3天，出席殖民政府主辦的慶「回歸」活動及殖民政府新班子就職儀式。黑警處長盧偉聰昨稱，黑警已作好充份準備。他指，有鑑於歐洲近日連環出現「孤狼式」恐襲，黑警屆時會以反恐規格佈防。<br />\n<br />\n對於有批評指示威區越設越遠，盧偉聰強調尊重市民言論和集會自由，但香港目前反恐工作形勢「非常嚴峻」，他呼籲示威者當日要保持和平理性，避免過激行為令警力耗散。"},{"pid":"c1cc9f3234faf56b622b681c939f0462c3c6df18","tid":296841,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T03:24:37.000Z","msg":"叫雜種咪撚嚟,咁你班友咪可以去蛇王下囉"},{"pid":"322aa8bac1d38e7f7fbe22cd7a1784f809328912","tid":296841,"uid":93986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T03:25:01.000Z","msg":"應該冇事發生<br />\n因為香港人普遍怕事"},{"pid":"a78731725f3306843f0a54cad741b87007564c21","tid":296841,"uid":427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T03:49:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a091e391263a485c879c7b4a5c3129710cdd7d5","tid":296841,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T03:49:41.000Z","msg":"你既職責黎喎"},{"pid":"69502766396bd688a65209bd90263c18908bd32e","tid":296841,"uid":342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T03:51:31.000Z","msg":"有冇孤狼？<br />\n<br />\n利申支持三跑 港珠澳大橋"},{"pid":"741980422a2eb021782866d2ea6aa94c92a70ee9","tid":296841,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T03:56:05.000Z","msg":"做乜唔叫啲蝻唔好強姦，叫啲蝗唔好打劫？"},{"pid":"26ebf151487ddbc4d6a9001dd4c29d94fb3afb33","tid":296841,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime